All rights reserved.

Contact
-------
jbenjamincook@gmail.com

To test the whole project, run the following line in an R session:

source("hardcore-model.R")

When the program finishes running, plots can be found in the 
hardcore-model/output folder and an animation can be found 
in hardcore-model/output/animation/animation.html.